^ Harmonia, Henry George Liddell, Robert Scott, "A Greek-English Lexicon", at Perseus
^ 3.0 3.1 Dahlhaus, Carl. Harmony. (編) Macy, Laura. Grove Music Online. Oxford Music Online. Oxford University Press.  
^ 4.0 4.1 4.2 4.3 Arnold Whittall, The Oxford Companion to Music, ed. Alison Latham, (Oxford University Press, 2002) (accessed via [Oxford Reference Online], 16 November 2007 is gayubview=Main&entry=t114.e3144 )
^ Harmony, §3: Historical development. Carl Dahlhaus. (編) Macy, Laura. Grove Music Online. Oxford Music Online. Oxford University Press.  
^ see also Whittall 'Harmony: 4. Practice and Principle', Oxford Companion to Music


